headline: Agoda Renews Partnership with Indonesia's Ministry of Tourism with a Brief to Boost Travel Growth
summary: Agoda, a digital travel platform, has renewed its partnership with Indonesia's Ministry of Tourism as the company continues to promote travel in one of Asia's most alluring destinations.
